OL,3,CChaotic crowds and arrest made after
OL,4,CCardiff Swatch shop disorder
OL,6,FPolice had to be called to Cardiff's
OL,7,Flargest shopping centre after crowds
OL,8,Fflooded inside to get their hands on a
OL,9,Flimited edition watch.
OL,11,FQueues of people gathered by the
OL,12,Fentrances of Cardiff's St Davids
OL,13,FCentre on Saturday morning as they
OL,14,Fhoped to get their hands on Swatch's
OL,15,Fnew Royal Pop collection.
OL,17,FThe rare accessory is a collaboration
OL,18,Fbetween Swatch and Audemars Piguet and
OL,19,Fwas only available in-store. A limit
OL,20,Fof one watch per person per day was
OL,21,Falso put in place to control stock.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/5
