OL,3,CChaotic crowds and arrest made after
OL,4,CCardiff Swatch shop disorder
OL,6,FThe #335 watch has sold for thousands
OL,7,Fof pounds on resale sites.
OL,9,FVideos online show crowds of fans
OL,10,Frushing towards Cardiff's Swatch store
OL,11,Fas people shout to "keep running".
OL,13,FAfter missing out on the watch, one
OL,14,Fman said he had been waiting since
OL,15,Fmidnight the night before.
OL,17,FSpeaking to Affluent Time's Youtube
OL,18,Fchannel, he explained that the rush of
OL,19,Fpeople was like being in a stampede:
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
