OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1779210357
OL,3,CChaotic crowds and arrest made after
OL,4,CCardiff Swatch shop disorder
OL,6,F"Everyone was getting crushed...people
OL,7,Fwere getting trampled on.
OL,9,F"I had to shield my son", he added.
OL,11,FAn arrest was also made during the
OL,12,Fchaos.
OL,14,FSouth Wales Police said they were
OL,15,Fcalled to St David's shopping centre
OL,16,Fon Saturday after reports that about
OL,17,F300 people were trying to get into the
OL,18,FSwatch store at 6.20am.
OL,20,FIn a statement, a spokesperson for
OL,21,FSouth Wales Police said:
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
