OL,3,CChaotic crowds and arrest made after
OL,4,CCardiff Swatch shop disorder
OL,6,F"A 25-year-old man from Pengam was
OL,7,Farrested and issued with a Section 35
OL,8,Fdispersal notice with the conditions
OL,9,Fthat they are not to enter Cardiff
OL,10,FCity Centre again during Saturday May
OL,11,F16."
OL,13,FThe high demand for Swatch's Royal Pop
OL,14,Fcollection has been seen across the
OL,15,FUK, with the company forced to close
OL,16,Ftheir shops nationwide on Saturday for
OL,17,Fthe safety of both customers and staff.
OL,19,FIn a statement posted on Facebook,
OL,20,FSwatch said:
