OL,3,CChaotic crowds and arrest made after
OL,4,CCardiff Swatch shop disorder
OL,6,F"In light of safety considerations for
OL,7,Fboth our customers and our staff"
OL,8,Fstores in Liverpool, Manchester,
OL,9,FBirmingham, Sheffield, Glasgow and
OL,10,FCardiff would be closed for the day,
OL,11,Falong with all of the London stores.
OL,13,F"The Royal Pop Collection will remain
OL,14,Favailable for several months."
